summary: This is a New York City Police Department Department of Motor Vehicles record executed on July 24, 2019, documenting vehicle registration details for a 2017 black Jeep. The document appears to be part of a property or asset record, possibly related to an investigation.

events.title: Vehicle Record Execution
events.description: A New York City Police Department Department of Motor Vehicles record was executed, documenting vehicle registration details.

keyFacts: A vehicle record was executed by the NYPD Department of Motor Vehicles on July 24, 2019.
The record documents a 2017 black Jeep with New York license plates.
The document is part of a property/asset record, possibly related to investigative activities.
